FBIS3-26591 "drchi027_n_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-027 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Feb 1994 Economic & Agricultural Li Peng Signs Decree on Work-Hour Regulations OW0902065994 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0700 GMT 7 Feb 94 OW0902065994 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service Language: Chinese Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, 7 Feb (XINHUA) -- Decree No. 146 of the State Council of the People's Republic of China: The "Regulations of the State Council on Working Hours for Staff Members and Workers" were passed at the 15th executive meeting of the State Council on 24 January 1994 and are hereby promulgated for implementation effective 1 March 1994. [Signed] Premier Li Peng [Dated] 3 February 1994
